本来家里留给她的房间慢慢地变成了“仓库”，堆放了家里各种物品，收拾起来也非常麻烦。 李先生是南京溧水人，在北京工作、成家，现在孩子也已经工作，定居北京二三十年，逢年过节回老家，也是选择了住酒店。 2月7日，现代快报记者采访发现， 酒店多个房型已经订完 扬州一家酒店多个房型在线上平台也显示已经订满。工作人员介绍， 华住集团数据显示，截至1月29日，2024年春节假期酒店预订率是去年春节假期期间预订率的近3倍，北京、上海、广州、深圳、泉州、哈尔滨、厦门、洛阳、柳州等城市在春节假期期间的预订率都迎来大涨。 来源：现代快报/现代+爆满！“过年回家不住家里住酒店”火上热搜_网友_房间_一家"},"attached_info":"CkAIlY2ZiMW3tcZvEAMaCTEwNTI5MjgwMyDA6pGuBjAAOOQEQAVyCTY0MzU2Nzg1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"533 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ece72f429ff691a36f32aebdc93761d9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"6_1707498843.707552","card_id":"Q_643793608","target":{"id":643793608,"title":"如何评价郭耘奇、谢泽成、闫佩伦等在 2024 年春晚表演的小品《开不了口》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/643793608","type":"question","created":1707487434,"answer_count":98,"follower_count":128,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[19801,727000,3165384],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIlY2ZiMW3tcZvEAMaCTEwNTM0Mjg4NiDK4ZiuBjAAOIABQAZyCTY0Mzc5MzYwOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"532 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9d9845de407d60454a19306c8346af1b_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1707498843.707785","card_id":"Q_643713609","target":{"id":643713609,"title":"如何评价 2024 年龙年春晚岳云鹏孙越表演的相声《我要不一样》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/643713609","type":"question","created":1707456792,"answer_count":423,"follower_count":482,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6134,10035,162305,436320,3296192],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIlY2ZiMW3tcZvEA